articles.title: F1 Singapore GP: Leclerc tops FP1 session interrupted by lizards - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Ferrari's Charles Leclerc and Carlos Sainz led Max Verstappen in FP1 at Formula 1's 2023 Singapore Grand Prix, which was interrupted three times by lizards traversing the Marina Bay track.
